{"tid":1017001,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"黃寶欣算唔算係俾黃翊條 MK 仔累到收皮 ?","createTime":"2019-02-11T07:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T14:04:24.000Z","uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3d47f7888428b4b33705ed01e9d16f4650ccf686","tid":1017001,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:14:31.000Z","msg":"當年黃寶欣明明係超級新人 , 冒起得好勁 , 無端端俾件半紅不黑嘅MK仔後輩溝 , 之後就急速收皮 , 無幾耐仲分埋手<br />\n<br />\n黃翊自己都收埋皮 , 但到而家都仲要講到係自己「唔要江山要美人」, 當時明明係黃寶欣紅過佢 , 正一累街坊<br />\n<br />\n講起黃寶欣多數只會諗起佢係亞視奀星 , 好慘<br />\n<br />\n註 : 當年同期目標對手有陳慧嫻"},{"pid":"454e5ebe49cf508c9e01588cb16c98fa6d4a98db","tid":1017001,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a494713e601fd665034fa30c98123ef270e927f","tid":1017001,"uid":84010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T20:17:47.000Z","msg":"黃翊同黃寶欣既人氣唔係都係差唔多咩<br />\n佢哋拍淘氣雙子星都係做配角<br />\n黃寶欣堅有實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d2_lfvDpvug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd2_lfvDpvug&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu163e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=85d2c16d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d2_lfvDpvug</a><br />\n紅歌唔紅人，轉唱片監製同唱片公司，冇固定形象，先係唔紅既因素，同黃翊拍拖影響唔大"},{"pid":"8d59e148015f547fcf6e636577d9a8e96a990f13","tid":1017001,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:57:50.000Z","msg":"黃寶欣早黃翊兩三年出道 , 個勢一直都唔錯 , 一識條 MK 就明顯走下坡"},{"pid":"a4989943d9280d6e795bff22a874912ff626966e","tid":1017001,"uid":84010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:58:28.000Z","msg":"黃翊邊似mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黃寶欣唔算係偶像派，拍拖有影響到人氣？<br />\n佢出咗兩隻碟之後搵咗周啟生做唱片監製<br />\n曲風同之前好大分別，轉咗歌路，聽眾覺得唔好聽自然就人氣下滑<br />\n周啟生風格好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj