tainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170318%2F56446401&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu163e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=fe4cfed0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170318%2F56446401&h=937d58de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20170318/56446401</a><br />\n黃寶欣話冇比飛圖雪<br />\n睇番佢係飛圖出既第一張唱片，公司嘥咁多錢宣傳，銷量得金唱片<br />\n當時唱片市道好，如果係新人仲接受到，但黃寶欣撈咗幾年，個勢仲一直跌<br />\n濃情好勁有雙白金，她是誰只得金唱片，佢就轉咗唱片監製，但都於事無補<br />\n你話佢係超級新人都係佢初出道出濃情時候，有hit歌酒杯敲鋼琴，之後無以為繼<br />\n就咁睇黃寶欣歌唱事業不斷跌，飛圖隻碟佢轉形象同歌路，銷量都嘛嘛，無力回天<br />\n飛圖幫又幫過，唔賣得就係唔賣得<br />\n覺得歌手冇叫座力冇前途，仲邊會比錢佢出碟同宣傳？既然唔出碟，拖到93年就解約都合理<br />\n如果飛圖隻碟賣到雙白金，仲會唔會解約？<br />\n<br />\n反觀黃翊當時上緊位，唱片公司捧佢做偶像派<br />\n佢一意孤行唔聽公司話被雪，錄緊碟都被逼stop，點睇都係佢傷d"},{"pid":"62cd2e32687ea16e9692f186cb359fd56103e23f","tid":1017001,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"53ed2df93609f6e72b14afa008e267f48475095d","tid":1017001,"uid":84010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a61ffd57b52fbe90cddee1193fba5d9677e4ebf6","tid":1017001,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a894c863e3b111c5913fb372e2fcbdafda060886","tid":1017001,"uid":84010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:42:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6pEWB_yu4AU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6pEWB_yu4AU&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu163e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=ddc90c0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6pEWB_yu4AU</a><br />\n黃寶欣話貼身情人出既時候(90年)，間唱片公司就快執<br />\n90-92年只出精選碟，佢唔受公司重視，間公司又就執，順其自然到92解約有咩問題，就咁睇唔關拍拖事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"講緊新公司飛圖幫佢出左一隻碟就解約，唔係舊公司銀星"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T15:31:06.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20170318/56446401\" data-sr-url=\"https